1
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,280
[Yue'er.]

2
00:00:24,719 --> 00:00:29,719
[Mom! Mom!]

3
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,320
[Who killed my mom?]

4
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:39,159
[I want revenge.]

5
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,600
[The fire]

6
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:52,280
[has been burning in my heart for 16 years.]

7
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:55,600
[Dad said I had to get stronger to get revenge.]

8
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:58,719
[I'm willing to do anything for that.]

9
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,959
I just got the news.

10
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:49,359
Black Snow Group will sabotage our signing ceremony

11
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:51,719
with the great artist Shuyun Hall next month.

12
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,719
Go and deal with this old friend of mine.

13
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,039
Over a decade ago,

14
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,159
somehow,

15
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,560
Jiang Changfa and his 3Z

16
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,560
suddenly took off,

17
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,560
leaving Black Snow far behind.

18
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:39,520
His only son Jiang Yue

19
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:40,919
even took out

20
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,960
over a dozen of our top experts.

21
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:43,879
Butterfly,

22
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:45,719
you're the top assassin on the Dark Web.

23
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,800
Please destroy 3Z for me.

24
00:02:52,479 --> 00:02:53,280
Jiang Yue.

25
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:57,680
Interesting.

26
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:01,360
I'll take this job.

27
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,360
The person who attacked me just now

28
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,519
is not to be underestimated.

29
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:07,720
Who exactly is he?

30
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,240
Butterfly.

31
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,439
This killer marked with a butterfly

32
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,399
and a butterfly mask

33
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,360
can always precisely lock onto

34
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,959
my whereabouts and transaction locations,

35
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,839
but never confronts me head-on.

36
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:03,720
Then I'll

37
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,680
lure you into the game.

38
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,879
Jiang Yue, you're a brave and strategic opponent.

39
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:13,560
It seems we need to have a direct showdown.

40
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:48,199
A battle between masters is indeed intriguing.

41
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,279
Move aside.

42
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:38,319
Stop following me.

43
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,360
Is that guy

44
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,199
your boyfriend?

45
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:18,439
A freak like her

46
00:08:18,439 --> 00:08:19,920
can't possibly have a boyfriend.

47
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:22,079
Are you a prostitute

48
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,959
or a kept woman?

49
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,679
Are you out of your mind?

50
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,080
You can fill your water,

51
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,120
but why scald Lu Luo?

52
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,519
Lu Qi, what did I do to you?

53
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,799
How dare you scald me!

54
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,399
Did that guy give you the courage?

55
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:16,200
I didn't expect

56
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,399
you to be so good at this.

57
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,759
How much do you charge for one night?

58
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,480
You filthy slut!

59
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:23,159
Didn't your father teach you how to behave?

60
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,600
Come here.

61
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,039
Come on.

62
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:30,879
Are you out of your mind?

63
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,519
Let's go.

64
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:54,720
Let's go.

65
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,919
Do you really need this?

66
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,000
They didn't make you

67
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:03,840
go to the new campus.

68
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,519
Get in the car.

69
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,120
We lost the fight.

70
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,120
If it weren't for you,

71
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:17,799
we would have won.

72
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,200
Is this the win you're talking about?

73
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:24,240
Don't bother.

74
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,600
I don't want to bother.

75
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,639
But my dad told me to do it.

76
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,000
From now on,

77
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:31,559
until your college entrance examination,

78
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,360
I'm your guardian.

79
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:35,320
I didn't expect you to be a daddy's girl.

80
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,799
Qi, come here.

81
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,240
Why don't you say hello?

82
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:49,879
Come here.

83
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,519
Qi, I know you like photography,

84
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,279
so I bought you a camera.

85
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,840
Do you like it?

86
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,120
Qi,

87
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,399
You want to apply for that school,

88
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,279
Zhangyi College, right?

89
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:08,320
I've looked into it for you.

90
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,480
It's at best a second-tier college.

91
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,799
Let's not apply to this school.

92
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:14,559
Go abroad after the college entrance examination.

93
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,000
I've paved the road for you.

94
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,720
Don't be unhappy.

95
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:21,799
Zhangyi College is my dad's alma mater.

96
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:28,480
Didn't we agree to take a family photo together?

97
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:29,480
Come on.

98
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,399
Yes.

99
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,679
Come here.

100
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:33,720
Let's take a family photo.

101
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:37,720
Jiang Yue.

102
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,320
Qi.

103
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,960
You two are brother and sister.

104
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:43,559
Get closer in the future.
